    "## 绗簲姝ワ細鍒涘缓 Agent\n",
    "\n",
    "LangChain 鎺ㄨ崘浣跨敤 **LangGraph** 椋庢牸鐨?`create_react_agent`锛屽畠瀹炵幇浜嗙粡鍏哥殑 **ReAct**锛圧easoning + Acting锛夊惊鐜細\n",
    "\n",
    "```\n",
    "Thought 鈫?Action 鈫?Observation 鈫?Thought 鈫?... 鈫?Final Answer\n",
    "```"
   ]
