     "text": [
      "鉁?LangGraph RAG 娴佹按绾挎瀯寤哄畬鎴怽n",
      "\n",
      "  cache_check 鈫?retrieve 鈫?rerank 鈫?generate 鈫?END\n",
      "  cache_check 鈫?END锛堝懡涓紦瀛樻椂锛塡n"
     ]
